              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 7.6*7.6 cm detector positioned with its front",
                "face 1 cm from the centre of the target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two detectors. An 85 cm3 detector, fixed at",
                "either 125 or 135 degr., was used to monitor the",
                "position of the resonance in the target by providing an",
                "accurate measurement of the Doppler shifted energy of a",
                "secondary gamma-ray transition. The second detector was",
                "a 60 cm3 intrinsic germanium detector which could be",
                "positioned at angles between 25 and 90 degr. to the",
                "beam direction for the measurement of gamma-ray angular",
                "distributions"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neon gas, enriched to greater than 99.99% in Ne-20.The",
                "target assembly was built into a 25 cm diameter",
                "stainless steel flange and consisted of a 5 cm long",
                "tube containing the target gas with 4 cm long nozzles",
                "at each end restricting the flow of gas out of the tube"
              ]
            }
